title: Creating a Hospital Tank for my Fish that Craps a Lot

media:group.media:title: Creating a Hospital Tank for my Fish that Craps a Lot
media:group.media:description:
Big Dookie 2.0 either got scratched up by getting pinned between sponge filters or the heater or just has body ulcers for whatever reason. Everyone else seems fine so I will put him in the hospital tank until he gets better. I hope this video helps anyone out there with a fish in need of a hospital tank.
